On 17 Oct 1994, R. Stewart Ellis wrote:
> Mark Crispin <mrc@CAC.Washington.EDU> writes:
>  >On 7 Oct 1994, Neil Rickert wrote:
>  >> The saved messages are separated by a "From " line.  News articles
